 (for [Section 2.4.2](../../parallel/openmp/2-4-2-sections-construct.md) on page 14) functions *xaxis*, *yaxis*, and *zaxis* can be executed concurrently. The first `section` directive is optional.  Note that all `section` directives need to appear in the lexical extent of the `parallel``sections` construct.  \n  \n```  \n#pragma omp parallel sections  \n{  \n    #pragma omp section  \n        xaxis();  \n    #pragma omp section  \n        yaxis();  \n    #pragma omp section  \n        zaxis();  \n}  \n```"}